cs.NI, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.RO, cs.GR 

This paper involves the use of UAVs for IoT sensing and VR/AR communication, which falls under the category of networked systems and communication (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the reconstruction of immersive scenes from captured data, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) techniques. The use of UAVs for spatial distribution and optimal power/link scheduling involves robotics (cs.RO) and graphics (cs.GR) as well.
